history.content: As in the title - I'll be taking CS 61C, EECS 149, and Physics 7B this fall, in addition to (hopefully) course staff and/or research. Is this a reasonable workload? I've heard 149 can be pretty light at the beginning of the semester and tougher at the end, so I don't want to end up completely swamped in the last month of the semester.
history.subject: 61C+149+7B workload
